 />\n唉 我真係好想番番以前</blockquote><br />\n報應"},{"pid":"9ebeb64f4633b3f8a68c722fa3c426d68c49b494","tid":53542,"uid":26581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n想回到過去"},{"pid":"2b88c9d0f02e7b472b6e1139b4dd8bd5061440a1","tid":53542,"uid":56888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n想回到過去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明白架，不過向前看啦！"},{"pid":"559447c3b14cf2461cb79e1910e0a70a0410c3f5","tid":53542,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:16:14.000Z","msg":"分左手幾年都仲係會間唔中諗起ex 發夢先見到佢真係好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}